title: Win10_EN-GBx64.ISO All Updates Integrated 4GB USB Key 23-03-2018
description: This is a Windows 10 X64 EN-GB install ISO. It has Windows 10 Pro, Home and Enterprise OS Build 16299.334. It is NOT cracked. You need to have installed Windows 10 before or have a valid licence key to use this ISO. No updates will install on a clean install other than Defender updates and the Malicious Software Tool. It will fit on a 4GB USB key. Use Rufus to make a GPT install key. https://rufus.akeo.ie/ The ISO was made from the Full Retail Consumer ESD file and the updates were integrated with 'W10UI_4.4' properly. To learn how to do all this yourself go to mydigitalife forums. No need to pirate Windows when you can get legit keys from eBay for about $10
